            <abstract>
                <p>A miniature illustrating <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3596Miracle"/> typically 
                    with as a sequence of seven episodes/events, showing: first, the youth Zakāryās fastening a crown of roses to an icon of <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/>; Zakāryās
                    praying the greeting of the angel before the icon of Mary, Zakāryās prosterning himself; the chief of the thieves hiding behind a tree; Zakāryās standing before
                    <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/>, who is sitting on a throne surrounded by angels, and collects roses out of his mouth; the thieves hiding behind trees;
                    the thieves being consecrated as monks.</p>
